data.description: Discover unmatched comfort and style in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem on a main road. This unique home, set on an expansive 1.01-acre lot, perfectly combines elegance and functionality. Step inside to find a thoughtfully laid out floor plan featuring a living room, a den with a cozy fireplace, and a flex room that can serve as an office or additional living space. Indulge in the master suite with a walk-in closet and a newly tiled en-suite bathroom for your private oasis. The kitchen, boasting granite countertops and contemporary tilework, is a culinary enthusiast's dream. Unwind in the den's indoor bar or bask in the year-round outdoor entertainment with the custom-built tiki bar, covered patio, and the delightful 14x14 pergola. The backyard, enclosed by a 6 to 8 ft stockade fence, guarantees privacy while hosting summer soirees. Notable upgrades include a rejuvenating hot tub, a modern 6-year-old HVAC system, double-paned windows, and an energy-efficient attic with sprayed insulation. The property also features a spacious 30x50 shop complete with a garage door opener and a 4-person corner infrared sauna. Extra amenities include a 2-year-old asphalt driveway, a 4-year-old well, and a 12x17 outside bonus room with a secret-bookshelf door leading to a vented basement that measures 12x16 underneath. This property truly presents a unique blend of luxury and practicality. SELLER WILL GIVE $1,000 DOLLAR ALLOWANCE TOWARD CLOSING COST OR HOME IMPROVEMENTS TO USE AS BUYER NEEDS.
